      "content": {
        "title": "Fasciotomy Technique and Complications",
        "definition": "Two-incision leg fasciotomy and forearm volar-dorsal release with wound management.",
        "summary": "Delayed fasciotomy risks Volkmann contracture; skin grafting often required for wound closure."
      },
